Package software.kes.kraftwerk.bias

Interface BiasSettings

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultPropertyTestingBiasSettings, EmptyBiasSettings
    public interface BiasSettings
    A collection of guidelines for injecting special values into the output of a Generator.

    This is a low-level concept that should only be of concern for authors of property-testing libraries, and not so much for users. See DefaultPropertyTestingBiasSettings.defaultPropertyTestBiasSettings() for a set of default value for property-testing purposed.

      • overrideWith

        default BiasSettings overrideWith​(BiasSettings other)
        Returns a new BiasSettings that is the same as this one, but with certain settings overridden.

        Any BiasSetting in other that is not BiasSetting.NoBias will override the setting found in this BiasSettings.

        Parameters:
        other - the other BiasSettings
        Returns:
        a BiasSettings
